### ==========================================
### 🎬 BlockBuster API - Tests
### ==========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@movieId = REEMPLAZAR_CON_ID_REAL

### ==========================================
### CRUD
### ==========================================

### Crear película - Terminator 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Terminator 2",
  "director": "James Cameron",
  "year": 1991,
  "genre": "scifi",
  "stock": 3
}

### Crear película - The Matrix
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix",
  "director": "Wachowski Sisters",
  "year": 1999,
  "genre": "scifi",
  "stock": 5
}

### Crear película - Superbad (comedia)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Superbad",
  "director": "Greg Mottola",
  "year": 2007,
  "genre": "comedy",
  "stock": 4
}

### Crear película duplicada (debe fallar 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix",
  "director": "Otro Director",
  "year": 2020,
  "genre": "action"
}

### Listar todas las películas
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies

### Filtrar por género (scifi)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?genre=scifi

### Filtrar por género (comedy)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?genre=comedy

### Obtener película por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}

### ==========================================
### ALQUILER
### ==========================================

### Alquilar película (1ª vez - debe funcionar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/rent

### Alquilar película (2ª vez)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/rent

### Alquilar película (3ª vez)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/rent

### Alquilar película (4ª vez - debe fallar si stock era 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/rent

### Devolver película
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/return

### Alquilar de nuevo (ahora debe funcionar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/rent

### ==========================================
### ESTADÍSTICAS
### ==========================================

### Top 5 más alquiladas
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/stats/top

### Top 3 más alquiladas
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/stats/top?limit=3

### ==========================================
### LIMPIEZA
### ==========================================

### Eliminar película
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}

### ==========================================
### CARÁTULAS
### ==========================================

### Subir carátula a una película
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/cover
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-cover.jpg
--boundary--

### Obtener carátula de una película
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/cover

### Obtener carátula de película sin carátula (debe fallar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/cover

### Subir carátula a película inexistente (debe fallar 404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/movies/000000000000000000000000/cover
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-cover.jpg
--boundary--

### ==========================================
### VALIDACIONES
### ==========================================

### Crear sin título (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "director": "Alguien",
  "year": 2020,
  "genre": "action"
}

### Crear con género inválido (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Película Rara",
  "director": "Director",
  "year": 2020,
  "genre": "musical"
}

### Crear con año futuro (debe fallar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Película del Futuro",
  "director": "Director",
  "year": 2099,
  "genre": "scifi"
}
